# Implementation Plan - Remove "Services" and Optimize Layout

This plan outlines the steps to remove all references to the "Services" section and optimize the header and hero sections for a more premium look.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Global Styles ([style.css](file:///c:/Users/BE1/Downloads/HAICCO%20WAB%20SITE/style.css))
- **Header (`nav`):** Update spacing, background, and shadow.
- **Logo (`.logo img`):** Reduce height to 70px.
- **Menu Typography (`.nav-links a`):** Apply uppercase, font-size 14px, and letter-spacing 1px.
- **Menu Spacing (`.nav-links`):** Set gap to 36px.
- **Hero Section (`.hero-section`):** Standardize padding, min-height, and alignment.
    - `padding-top: 160px;` (Balanced for fixed header)
    - `min-height: 100vh;`
    - `display: flex; align-items: center;`

### 2. Homepage ([index.html](file:///c:/Users/BE1/Downloads/HAICCO%20WAB%20SITE/index.html))
- **Navigation:** Remove "Services" link.
- **Content:** Delete the entire `<section class="services-grid">`.
- **Footer:** Remove "Services Techniques" link.

### 3. All Other HTML Pages
- **Navigation:** Remove "Services" link from:
    - [contact.html](file:///c:/Users/BE1/Downloads/HAICCO%20WAB%20SITE/contact.html)
    - [projets.html](file:///c:/Users/BE1/Downloads/HAICCO%20WAB%20SITE/projets.html)
    - [projet-1.html](file:///c:/Users/BE1/Downloads/HAICCO%20WAB%20SITE/projet-1.html) to [projet-6.html](file:///c:/Users/BE1/Downloads/HAICCO%20WAB%20SITE/projet-6.html)
    - [solutions-energetiques.html](file:///c:/Users/BE1/Downloads/HAICCO%20WAB%20SITE/solutions-energetiques.html)
    - [solutions-ia.html](file:///c:/Users/BE1/Downloads/HAICCO%20WAB%20SITE/solutions-ia.html)
- **Footer:** Remove "Services Techniques" link (where present).
- **Hero Layout:** Remove inline `style="padding-top: ...; min-height: ...;"` from `<header>` or `<section>` tags to rely on the updated global CSS.

### 4. File Deletion
- **Delete [services.html](file:///c:/Users/BE1/Downloads/HAICCO%20WAB%20SITE/services.html)**

---

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Not applicable for this static site.

### Manual Verification
1. **Link Integrity:** Click through all navigation links to ensure no "Services" references remain and no 404s occur.
2. **Visual Consistency:** Verify the header is more compact (70px logo) and the hero title doesn't collide with the fixed header.
3. **Responsiveness:** Check the layout on mobile (width < 768px) to ensure the header remains functional and spacing is appropriate.
4. **Content Check:** Ensure the "Services" section is completely gone from the homepage.
5. **Space Balance:** Ensure the H1/H2 titles have professional vertical spacing.
